data.description: Still time to get in here BEFORE the New Year!    Here is the perfect home for you. This 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath is ready for you to make it your own. This home was built in 2022 and sits on .28 acres. The kitchen features a large island with plenty of storage for all your cooking supplies and easy entertainment. There is a versatile space on the main level that can be used as a home office or spare bedroom. The second floor hosts the primary suite with a large walk-in closet. There are three additional bedrooms with plenty of storage. All bedrooms have been prewired for ceiling fans of your choice. This well constructed home includes dedicated circuit in the garage for a second Refrigerator or Freezer for extra food storage. You will enjoy an easy move into a worry- free home that include stainless steel refrigerator. Home already wired for ADT security and cameras will convey.   Remaining builders 2-year warranty on Electrical and Plumbing, along with remaining 10-year structural warranty. Shingles have a 25-year warranty through manufacturer. Come see this home today before its gone.    1% Lender Credit for Qualified Buyers using Preferred Lender. Use this for rate buydown or closing costs. You Chose!
